data.description: Discover the epitome of rustic elegance in this exceptional listing. Nestled amidst sprawling rolling pastures, this remarkable property features three bedrooms and one bathroom. A shop house, turn-out pen, and stalls make it an ideal sanctuary for equestrian enthusiasts.Step inside and be captivated by the exquisite details that adorn this home. The kitchen showcases stunning granite countertops and a subway tile backsplash, perfectly complementing the rustic wood walls and rock features throughout.The open-concept living area boasts a vaulted ceiling, creating a sense of grandeur and spaciousness. Large windows flood the interior with natural light, offering breathtaking panoramic views of the surrounding landscape. Imagine waking up to the beauty of rolling hills and vibrant sunsets every day.The painted concrete slab floor adds a unique touch, seamlessly blending modern design with the rustic aesthetic. This property truly exemplifies the best of both worlds. Enjoy the warmth and character of rustic wood walls while relishing the convenience of modern amenities.Beyond the home itself, a gated entrance ensures privacy and security, providing peace of mind. Whether you seek solitude or plan to entertain guests, this property offers the perfect setting for both.Don't miss the opportunity to own this one-of-a-kind ''shouse'' (shop house) that combines country living with modern luxury. Embrace the tranquility of the rolling pastures, bask in the natural light that fills the interior, and indulge in the unique charm of this remarkable property.
